            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/36242047/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/36242047/" class="">完本</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/80283476/" class=" " title="天天读书">天天读书</a>
                (IT人好读书时而求甚解时而不求)
              
                <span class="allstar30" title="还行"></span>
